title: Amy Got Another Bizarre Delivery to Her House + Sounds from the 90’s Game! + Callers Who Share Name as Celebrities And What Life Is Like as Abraham Lincoln
itunes:title: Amy Got Another Bizarre Delivery to Her House + Sounds from the 90’s Game! + Callers Who Share Name as Celebrities And What Life Is Like as Abraham Lincoln
description:
Amy shares another random, crazy thing that showed up to her house and now we are concerned if they are all connected. We play a sound from the 90’s and the show has to guess what it’s from. Bobby talks about a story where a guy has to convince people his real name is Harry Potter. Callers share their stories of what life is like being named after famous people.
